me sobresaltó.

00:10:18.097 --> 00:10:19.258
Nada interesante.

00:10:20.378 --> 00:10:21.578
Vamos.

00:10:51.417 --> 00:10:52.378
Soy Nan Ruzhen,

00:10:53.417 --> 00:10:54.338
