elegante y elegante,

00:17:27.738 --> 00:17:28.938
simple y poco mundano,

00:17:29.698 --> 00:17:30.897
inteligente sin ser tímido,

00:17:31.417 --> 00:17:32.657
resiliente pero no impaciente.

00:17:33.338 --> 00:17:34.338
